d folder, containing a file with permission 600\r\n2. wait until the file is uploaded\r\n3. change the file on the server (ie using notes-app) or on another client\r\n4. wait until the file is downloaded\r\n5. permissions are 644\r\n\r\n### server configuration\r\noperating system: debian wheezy\r\n\r\nweb server: \r\n\r\nserver version: apache/2.2.22 (debian)\r\nserver built:   mar  4 2013 22:05:16\r\n\r\ndatabase: mysql \r\n\r\nmysqld  ver 5.5.31-0+wheezy1 for debian-linux-gnu on x86_64 ((debian))\r\n\r\nphp version: \r\n\r\nphp 5.4.4-14+deb7u5 (cli) (built: oct  3 2013 09:24:58) \r\n\r\n\r\nowncloud version:\r\n\r\n5.0.12\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nfile encryption is activated on the server\r\n\r\n\r\n### client configuration\r\n\r\nbrowser: none - desktop sync client\r\n\r\noperating system: ubuntu 13.04\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"cxxxx","id":1249406,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/401bfe4caac31871cf5be49649598576?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fb031bc612c61b4d8f14dc91808055dbc.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"401bfe4caac31871cf5be49649598576","url":"https://api.github.com/users/cxxxx","html_url":"https://github.com/cxxxx","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cxxxx/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cxxxx/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cxxxx/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cxxxx/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cxxxx/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cxxxx/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cxxxx/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cxxxx/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/cxxxx/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false}}